d.company

Class CompanyDBDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • d.company.CompanyDBDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompanyDAO

    public class CompanyDBDAO
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompanyDAO
    This class connects the Java program to the Derby Database. Includes the CRUD methods and methods for getting coupons/coupon lists for a specific company. This DBDAO layer knows to translate the outcome to Java beans or to collections.
